    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all project lovers and DIY mechanics! This car is ready for a complete transformation and offers a fantastic canvas for someone looking to build something special from the ground up. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it's a budget-friendly way to get started on your next automotive adventure!",
