    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously preserved. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine, and the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, with the engine and transmission operating as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Every feature and electronic component works exactly as intended, making this an exceptional find for a collector or a discerning buyer seeking a perfect example of this model.",
      "price": 48000.0,
